<div style="text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width: 400px; display:inline-block; text-align: left;">
        <nav>
            <img src="{{{hostAddress}}}/logo.png" alt="in a long time logo"></img>
        </nav>
    <h3>{{senderName}} sent you a {contentType}!</h3>
    <p>On {{nextSendDate}}, {{senderName}} from the past sent you a {{contentType}}. It was originally sent to another email, 
        but the sender listed this email as the backup email. Click the button below to view it.</p>
        <button style="background-color:purple; color:white; border:0px; padding:10px; border-radius:5px; !important">
            <a  href="{{{hostAddress}}}/future/{{{id}}}"
            style="color:white !important; text-decoration:none !important;"
            onMouseOver="this.style.color='white'"
            onMouseOut="this.style.color='white'">View {{contentType}}</a>
    </button>
</div>
</div>